==Demographics==
At the [[2020 United States Census|2020 census]], there were 52 people, 16 households, and 10 families living in the CDP. The population density was 50 people per square mile. There were 30 housing units.

The median household income was $20,587. The per capita income for the CDP was $13,461.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arizona.hometownlocator.com/az/pima/anegam.cfm |publisher=Arizona.hometownlocator.com |access-date=2021-09-07 |date=2021 |title=Ventana, AZ Profile: Facts & Data}}</ref>

